{"ts":"2026-07-13T22:19:34.239Z","author":"codex-root","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/547\n\nThis is backlog tracking only in the current immutable-history/read implementation lane. Reuse the public output contracts and avoid package-specific sentinels."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-f38n"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-547: SDK exporters and renderers cannot suppress host rendering of handled output"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Track the SDK contract gap where a package-owned exporter or renderer cannot explicitly mark a handled result as already emitted, causing host rendering to corrupt stdout or forcing stderr workarounds."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["area:extensions","area:output","area:sdk","gh-issue","package-authoring"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-13T22:19:34.239Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T22:19:34.239Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":180},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"A typed, documented suppression contract is shared by exporter, renderer, service override, CLI, and MCP dispatch; default behavior remains backward compatible; runtime and package-harness tests cover handled output, suppressed output, JSON/TOON, errors, and telemetry; a packed temp package proves stdout remains uncorrupted"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-ugqx"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/reporter","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/severity","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/repro_steps","value":"Implement a package exporter or renderer that streams or writes its own output, return a normal handled result, and observe the host render the result again because no public suppression sentinel exists."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/expected_result","value":"Public typed SDK contracts let handled exporter, renderer, and output-service paths explicitly suppress duplicate host rendering while preserving structured results, telemetry, and JSON/TOON contract clarity."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/actual_result","value":"Package authors must corrupt stdout with duplicate output, misuse stderr, or return shapes that the host still renders."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/component","value":"SDK exporter, renderer, and output service contracts"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/customer_impact","value":"Package authors cannot safely implement streaming, binary, or already-rendered export workflows through public SDK primitives."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-ixoa","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-13T22:19:34.239Z"},{"id":"pm-srns","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-13T22:19:34.239Z"},{"id":"pm-usfg","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-13T22:19:34.239Z"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-13T22:19:34.239Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Duplicate check 2026-07-14: all-status searches for GH-547, suppress host rendering, exporter renderer suppression, and stdout corruption found no existing item. GitHub issue #547 is canonical external evidence; this item is deliberately left open and unclaimed."}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"f3b21ec86ffe4e337969b0d226e68abefbdb116c0e77ee74e2308be3486a8674","message":""}
